JOIN
====

Usage: join

Join a guild when standing in a guild hall. Each guild grants access to
different skills and abilities.

To join a guild:
  1. Go to the guild hall (e.g., /world/guilds/fighters)
  2. Type 'join'

You can be a member of multiple guilds simultaneously, though some guilds
may have conflicts or requirements.

See also: leave, guilds, skills
